The paper deals with energy harvesting, communication, and control, which are all topics that fall under the umbrella of information theory (cs.IT). The use of reinforcement learning and multi-agent systems suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also deals with networking and communication protocols, which could place it in the categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY).
